com.verygoodsecurity.vgscollect.view.card

Class CardBrand

  • com.verygoodsecurity.vgscollect.view.card.CardBrand

  • public class CardBrand

    The data class definition for represent custom card brand. It may be useful to add new brands in addition to already defined brands or override existing ones.

        The data class definition for represent custom card brand. It may be useful to add new brands in addition to already defined brands or override existing ones.

        Parameters:
        regex - The regex rules for detection card brand.
        cardBrandName - The name of current card brand. This name may be visible for users.
        drawableResId - The drawable resource represents credit card logo.
        params - The set of parameters for card brand creation.
